<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="TVM3.2.11">
<l>uyirka ḷellā vulakamu muṭaiyavaṉai</l>
<l>kuyilkoḷ cōlait teṉkurukūrc caṭakōpaṉ</l>
<l>ceyirilcol licaimālai yāyirattu ḷippattu</l>
<l>muyiriṉmē lākkai yūṉiṭai yoḻivikkumē</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>These ten among the thousand in the flawless musical world garland</l>
<l>of Caṭakōpaṉ from southern Kurukūr with groves that have coels</l>
<l>on the one who possesses all the worlds with the living being</l>
<l>further puts an end to the souls’ bodies in the flesh.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
